Areas best suited for a National Marine Conservation Area (NMCA)

1. Recombine all MSA 4A SHPs using "Merge" from files located in: OG Files // MAEP GIS // polygons // Importance

2. Terrestrial areas removed by using "Erase" + land_parcel_poly_Merge_v2 - new layer in RB KC Clipped Polygons GDB // msa_4A_erase
